key.description: Unique name of the Cost Category.

matchOptions.description: Match options that you can use to filter your results. MatchOptions is only applicable for actions related to cost category. The default values for MatchOptions is `EQUALS` and `CASE_SENSITIVE`. Valid values are: `EQUALS`,  `ABSENT`, `STARTS_WITH`, `ENDS_WITH`, `CONTAINS`, `CASE_SENSITIVE`, `CASE_INSENSITIVE`.

values.description: Specific value of the Cost Category.
